text.0:
WHO helped Indonesia 🇮🇩 conduct a stakeholder review to evaluate & improve its #COVID19 health sector response, aligning it with the WHO Strategic Preparedness and Response Plan.

More details 👉https://t.co/Htmwib83Ww #WHOImpact https://t.co/DAI0XSWvB6
text.1:
WHO, @moh_srilanka 🇱🇰 & Sri Lankan College of Microbiologists have designed a set of training modules for #HealthcareWorkers on infection prevention & control guidelines related to #COVID19.

Available in 3 languages: Sinhala, Tamil & English

👉https://t.co/fKO4KnqyoF #WHOImpact https://t.co/Y0WaehYDiJ
